{"tid":34631,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴絲打可以幫我搵返個舊電視廣告","createTime":"2016-12-11T14:49:34.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-11T14:51:13.000Z","uid":34311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f07a384d21abc1a818b6df780bec7b2617515aca","tid":34631,"uid":34311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T14:49:35.000Z","msg":"個電視廣告大約係01至03年，我唔係好記得exactly係邊年<br />\n<br />\n咁個廣告大概係有兩隻狗(老母同仔)一齊行嘅，跟住隻狗bb百厭走咗個紙箱，之後個紙箱俾人執咗落架貨van(條友冇留意有隻狗喺入面，可能因為個紙箱&ldquo;cum&rdquo;埋咗)<br />\n<br />\n之後架貨van開走，狗媽媽發現個仔喺架貨van度，跟住係咁追<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲打記得呢個廣告係咩嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個廣告真係童年陰影嚟，睇親都喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0af86e8cbbeef4932e1e87852eb9d7ffb40cafd9","tid":34631,"uid":34311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T14:51:13.000Z","msg":"定係其實唔係廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}